reviewText: Bought as a gift for my husband.  He likes being able to watch an episode when he thinks about it, or a whole season if he wants to.
Love the archer series, delivery was very fast. I thought it was bluray but that was my mistake.
The best adult animated show to date!
I enjoy Archer.  The program has beautiful cartoon art and excellent writers. The defined personalities of the characters fuel the comedic situations and the hilarious dialogue.
Archer kicks ass !!! Very funny and the animation is very well done

Archer is an awesome series about a smart-in-all-the-wrong-ways Secret Agent Sterling Archer who works for the Isis Agency. This series is hilarious, it's definitely crude and ridiculous but it's made for adults so expect adult issues and conversations. The box set seems a bit overpriced but the series itself is wonderful and worth having permanently in your collection.
Why spend 99$ on this when you can buy them individually for 45$?
